{"tid":668273,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[Running U] 因為粉絲一句話，IU就突然把鞋子脫掉在慶生會上狂奔","createTime":"2018-05-17T13:00:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-21T00:30:28.000Z","uid":34643,"like":57,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"3ff6c6ff4b3fb77b37a5be78442c2115dcd54b14","tid":668273,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T13:00:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/e2nRz6ZR45g?t=74\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fe2nRz6ZR45g%3Ft%3D74&d=NE8Lr1bIN6vmzfkdjRnNrbIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=83cd4fc7\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/e2nRz6ZR45g?t=74</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在〈Palette（ ）〉中唱著「I like it I'm twenty five」的IU李知恩，在昨天滿25歲了！被公認是「粉絲傻瓜第一名」、寵粉寵出名的他，生日也當然是跟粉絲一起度過啦！在首爾樂天世界塔舉辦的「小型慶生粉絲會」當天，IU穿上透膚淡綠色飄逸洋裝、白色高跟鞋、浪漫編發散發清純美，走上舞台亮相的壽星大人根本是仙女下凡，但是明明應該充美美的女神飯拍、影片，卻被捕捉到他突然赤腳狂奔的畫面，到底是發生什麼事了？（笑）<br />\n<br />\n「IU」25歲生日粗卡嘿！！！小型粉絲會現場！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://t11.baidu.com/it/u=1603287967,257472815&amp;fm=173&amp;app=25&amp;f=JPEG?w=640&amp;h=347&amp;s=671411C75E8DB88CB9D180DA03008037\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft11.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D1603287967%2C257472815%26fm%3D173%26app%3D25%26f%3DJPEG%3Fw%3D640%26h%3D347%26s%3D671411C75E8DB88CB9D180DA03008037&h=953273f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://t10.baidu.com/it/u=3924063204,4041446606&amp;fm=173&amp;app=25&amp;f=JPEG?w=640&amp;h=349&amp;s=27049B475286A2BCCB218DDF03008013\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft10.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3924063204%2C4041446606%26fm%3D173%26app%3D25%26f%3DJPEG%3Fw%3D640%26h%3D349%26s%3D27049B475286A2BCCB218DDF03008013&h=cf39889e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在現場IU開始進行介紹「個人履歷書」的環節，撕掉「特技」那格答案時，居然出現特技是跑步（ ），大家還記得IU在《孝利家民宿》擔任打工仔的時候的「小跑步」模樣嗎？跑步時也常常身體比腳步前面，結果IU說：「這次在韓劇《我的大叔》中飾演的角色李至安拍攝時真的很跑了很多步，發現我真的跑步變快了很多」，一講完粉絲馬上質疑聲四起，IU馬上不服輸說「那我現在立刻跑給你們看！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://t12.baidu.com/it/u=4261355717,4235510201&amp;fm=173&amp;app=25&amp;f=JPEG?w=639&amp;h=346&amp;s=21541B6EEF69041DC048950A0300E092\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft12.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D4261355717%2C4235510201%26fm%3D173%26app%3D25%26f%3DJPEG%3Fw%3D639%26h%3D346%26s%3D21541B6EEF69041DC048950A0300E092&h=90cb2251&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://t12.baidu.com/it/u=2588863019,3278740166&amp;fm=173&amp;app=25&amp;f=JPEG?w=639&amp;h=346&amp;s=6574CB6EC43CA37406C9950A0300A083\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft12.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D2588863019%2C3278740166%26fm%3D173%26app%3D25%26f%3DJPEG%3Fw%3D639%26h%3D346%26s%3D6574CB6EC43CA37406C9950A0300A083&h=fdab7a20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://t10.baidu.com/it/u=2332716159,3982571337&amp;fm=173&amp;app=25&amp;f=JPEG?w=640&amp;h=348&amp;s=65745B6EBEEDA3745CC1651B0300E081\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft10.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D2332716159%2C3982571337%26fm%3D173%26app%3D25%26f%3DJPEG%3Fw%3D640%26h%3D348%26s%3D65745B6EBEEDA3745CC1651B0300E081&h=41585e5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n預備跑步時，一名男粉絲喊出：「很危險，把鞋子脫掉吧！」 IU也真的一秒脫下高跟鞋，還搭配小熱身拉腿、助跑小跳躍，真的超認真的要來跑一下（笑），跑完還跟大家說：「我真的跑步很快吧！是真的跑步變快了！」超可愛又寵粉的互動，圈粉力果然超狂！"},{"pid":"ad56721db969bfddb31c233c476825bd026cccd6","tid":668273,"uid":58140,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T13:01:19.000Z","msg":"好Q呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6617ff2fb8dba03246b16d98b82d4712285431b","tid":668273,"uid":34643,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T13:05:03.000Z","msg":"呢D先叫偶像"},{"pid":"5464ab4167881f84100a6e03d952e2a98a1cf3f7","tid":668273,"uid":34643,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T14:16:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://ww4.sinaimg.cn/large/006ajBdMgy1fre08ixvpoj30nm0vi774.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fww4.sinaimg.cn%2Flarge%2F006ajBdMgy1fre08ixvpoj30nm0vi774.jpg&h=0d014f97&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":